---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import { modelShort } from '../../platforms';
import KofiButton from '../../components/KofiButton.astro';
const releases=(await getCollection('releases')).sort((a,b)=>b.data.updated.valueOf()-a.data.updated.valueOf());
---
<Base title="Arcanum Originals — Downloadable AI RPG Engines | Arcanum RPGs" description="Original game engines built by Arcanum. Download the files, load them into ChatGPT, Claude, or Gemini, and play deeply-crafted worlds you won't find anywhere else.">
  <div class="wrap browse">
    <h1>Arcanum Originals</h1>
    <p class="sub">Our own packaged worlds. Download the files, load them into your AI, and play
    systems built with an obsessive level of detail — not available anywhere else.</p>
    <div class="grid">
      {releases.map(r=>(
        <a class="card" href={`/arcanum-games/${r.id}`}>
          <div class="thumb">{r.data.cover && <img src={r.data.cover} alt={r.data.title} loading="lazy" width="800" height="450"/>}</div>
          <div class="body">
            <div class="models">{r.data.models.map(m=> <span class="token is-platform">{modelShort(m)}</span>)}</div>
            <h2>{r.data.title}</h2>
            <p class="tag">{r.data.tagline}</p>
            <div class="foot mono"><span>{r.data.genres.slice(0,3).join(' · ')}</span><span class="dl">↓ {r.data.files.length} files</span></div>
          </div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="support">
      <p>All games are free to play on your own AI. If they gave you a good session:</p>
      <KofiButton />
    </div>
    <div class="about-strip">
      <p>Arcanum Originals are complete, engineered RPG systems — not character cards, not bare prompts. Each one is a master prompt plus a world knowledge file, designed together to run a specific kind of campaign with real mechanical depth and world consistency across long sessions.</p>
      <p>The kingdom-builder tracks your domain, your treasury, and the social hierarchy you navigate on the way to power. The relationship RPG tracks companion goals, trust, and emotional state without a single visible meter. The mature open-world adventure enforces dice-less tactical combat across a three-layer cosmology. The space-trading survival sim tracks cargo, customs heat, and reactor temperature in genuine tension with each other.</p>
      <p>All four are free to download and play on ChatGPT, Claude, or Gemini — load the files into your existing AI and play worlds you will not find anywhere else.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <style>
    .browse{padding:3rem 1.25rem 2rem;}
    h1{font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem);font-weight:600;}
    .sub{color:var(--parchment-dim);margin:.4rem 0 2rem;max-width:42rem;}
    .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1.2rem;}
    @media(min-width:700px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}}
    .card{border:1px solid var(--ember-soft);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--ink-2);color:var(--parchment);transition:border-color .18s,transform .18s;}
    .card:hover{border-color:var(--ember);text-decoration:none;transform:translateY(-2px);}
    .thumb{aspect-ratio:16/9;background:var(--ink);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
    .thumb img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;}
    .body{padding:1.2rem 1.4rem;}
    .models{display:flex;gap:.4rem;margin-bottom:.7rem;}
    .card h2{font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.4rem;}
    .tag{color:var(--parchment-dim);font-size:.96rem;}
    .foot{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:.72rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;color:var(--rune);margin-top:1rem;}
    .dl{color:var(--ember);}
    .support{margin-top:2.4rem;padding-top:2rem;border-top:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.2rem;flex-wrap:wrap;}
    .support p{color:var(--parchment-dim);font-size:.92rem;margin:0;}
    .about-strip{margin-top:2.4rem;padding-top:2rem;border-top:1px solid var(--line);max-width:760px;}
    .about-strip p{color:var(--parchment-dim);font-size:.98rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:.9rem;}
    .about-strip p:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
  </style>
</Base>
